definitions.definition: Any (member) of several species of birds in the genera Aburria , Chamaepetes , Oreophasis , Penelope , Penelopina , and Pipile , of the family Cracidae , limited to the Americas .

main_definition: Any (member) of several species of birds in the genera Aburria , Chamaepetes , Oreophasis , Penelope , Penelopina , and Pipile , of the family Cracidae , limited to the Americas .
